data.description: Stunning custom-built country charm with city convenience. Set on well over an acre this irrigated horse property has room for everything! 2000 sq/ft detached garage w/ office, half bath, car lift and feed room! The residence has a large finished basement with a bathroom. Custom craftsmanship including woodwork, trim, and crown molding throughout. Amazing brick entry.Living room features a brick fireplace, surround sound, & built-in bookshelves with disguised basement entry. Chef's kitchen w/ tray ceiling, top of the line  SS appliances, ice maker, warming drawer granite counters, custom cabinetry, a walk-in pantry and large island. Spacious master with fireplace, custom closet and generous bathroom w/ jetted tub. Additional bedrooms are also good size. Beautiful outdoor space with gazebo For a touch of coziness, the primary bedroom offers a personal fireplace, making it a perfect winter retreat! Its lavish ensuite has a separate tub/shower, two vanities w/vessel sinks, and a walk-in closet w/built-ins. Not to be outdone, the carpeted finished basement exudes versatility! Accentuated by a charming fireplace and a full bathroom, this space stands ready to be transformed according to your desires - entertainment or fitness needs. Laundry room with sink, cabinetry, and a desk. Check out the HUGE backyard that has been tastefully divided! A covered patio, mature trees, artificial turf, built-in seats, well-laid pavers, and a large Gazebo complete the picture. Beyond the fence, you'll find an expansive grassy area and stalls for your animals. You'll LOVE this place!
